snippet.title: Ultimate Rivals: The Court - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
With over 100 superstars from the NHL, NBA, WNBA, NFL, MLB, and US Women’s National Soccer Team, Ultimate Rivals: The Court gives YOU the chance to create a powerhouse basketball squad like never before!

Ultimate Rivals: The Court… coming soon to Apple Arcade and Steam. Add to your Steam wishlist now https://store.steampowered.com/app/1539400/Ultimate_Rivals_The_Court/ or visit https://www.ultimaterivals.com/ for more information.
